{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 1215297, "nreplies": 7, "sticky": 0, "user": "LoreAddict", "body": "Does he have special dialog if you have [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=19019]Thunderfury, Blessed Blade of the Windseeker[/url] equipped like the Shade of Aran if you had Medivh's staff?", "date": "2010-12-08T14:59:22-06:00", "rating": 80, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Yeah because wearing Atiesh during Shade was sensible too, and level 40s all had Corrupted Ashbringer in SM.  It's about flavour, not practicality.", "creationdate": "2010-12-13T02:22:12-06:00", "id": 202931, "rating": 52, "commentid": 1215297, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "260614", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Pro Tip: You can swap weapons in combat.", "creationdate": "2010-12-17T09:36:27-06:00", "id": 204887, "rating": 98, "commentid": 1215297, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "oberondreaming", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Imagine, if you will, you had a son.  And because you loved your son so much, you gave him a badass sword.  After sending him out into the world to do wind elemental stuff, some mortals killed him and stole his sword.  You grieve for a while, and eventually come to terms with your loss.  Then, year later, a group of mortals come in to your realm to kill you, and one of them has your son's sword in their possesion.  You are right, I am sure he would be totally cool about it.", "creationdate": "2011-01-01T03:35:06-06:00", "id": 210523, "rating": 127, "commentid": 1215297, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "16212", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Aran never had