{"commentv2": 1, "number": 9, "id": 1248883, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "LoreAddict", "body": "If this [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ReG4OshuW9g]video[/url] from the cataclysm beta is to be believed, the Heroic version of Al'Akir is [i]obscenely[/i] hard. \r\n\r\nA premade group decked out in the best gear available is incappable of clearing [i][b][u]phase one.[/u][/b][/i]\r\n\r\n...\r\n\r\nI sincerely don't know if I should be awed or terrified.", "date": "2010-12-20T20:57:19-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Both awe and terror. But taking a page from the guy narrating the action on that video, I'm excited that content appears to be this challenging -- I mean you heard the guy, he was practically ecstatic that \"this boss is unbeatable\" right now. It's nice to hear that many players are still chomping at the bit for a challenge. Can't wait to see which guild develops an effective strategy and manages to implement it.", "creationdate": "2010-12-21T14:22:55-06:00", "id": 469399, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1248883, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Lasengnomad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Phase one is the hardest phase, the rest is a cakewalk.  And it's not hard because of DPS, tanking, or healing, but because people need to dodge !@#$ properly. I imagine it's much harder to dodge *!@# on heroic.", "creationdate": "2011-01-07T00:27:08-06:00", "id": 473105, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1248883, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "DrakeWurrum", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 10, "id": 1249580, "nreplies": 7, "sticky": 0, "user": "583527", "body": "It seems that Deathwing has friends...\r\n<Insert sunglasses>\r\n...In high places.\r\n\r\nYEAAAAAAH!", "date": "2010-12-21T04:08:11-06:00", "rating": 366, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I hope that with that comment you're not just... *puts on sunglasses* ..Blowing hot air?", "creationdate": "2011-01-31T03:58:59-06:00", "id": 220447, "rating": 124, "commentid": 1249580, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "GrregPaxxton", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Now that this boss has been killed on heroic, you could say *sunglasses* ...he's gone with the wind.   YEAAAHHHH", "creationdate": "2011-01-31T20:52:20-06:00", "id": 220646, "rating": 163, "commentid": 1249580, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Sleepingfire", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I just downed him for the first time. Things have changed since the 4.2 patch.  Half the raid knew nothing going in, and we one-shotted him.  I guess at this point, you could say he's... *sunglasses* ... a breeze?", "creationdate": "2011-07-28T23:42:38-05:00", "id": 255304, "rating": 61, "commentid": 1249580, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "link55557", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Wow this boss is giant. He sure *sunglasses* blew me away.", "creationdate": "2012-08-28T03:42:27-05:00", "id": 566875, "rating": 12, "commentid": 1249580, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "950815", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body"