{"commentv2": 1, "number": 25, "id": 1326462, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "pierakor", "body": "It helped me a lot to zoom out as far as you can, a guildie told me to use the [b]\"/console cameraDistanceMax <value>\" and \"/console cameraDistanceMaxFactor <value>\"[/b] commands ingame and try out a few different settings, for ranged dps it helped a great deal noticing the sqaull lines in time and avoiding those moments when you have to dodge a squall line and get close to the boss because of wind burst at the same time.", "date": "2011-02-08T03:49:14-06:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 26, "id": 1335849, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "nosound", "body": "Getting knocked off the platform while in hard mode is fatale. \r\nGetting grabbed by tornadoes in hard mode is fatale (priests can still drag you out of tornado though).\r\nEven on normal mode it's refreshing my memories of how hard the fight with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/npc=11502]another Elemental Lord[/url] was.\r\nThanks Blizzard for creating an encounter, which is actually interesting and challenging even on normal difficulty.\r\n\r\nP.S. One of encounters in Cataclysm, which is MUCH harder on 25-man version, than it is on 10-man.", "date": "2011-02-14T09:56:31-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
