{"commentv2": 1, "number": 40, "id": 1428598, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Alisarian", "body": "[quote]By Spadge 11 days ago (Patch 4.1.0)\nI've heard that the drop chance for helm and shoulders is very low. Can anyone confirm or deny this?[/quote]\n\nI don't think so. Maybe it's a bit lower than from Nef or Cho'gall but not 2%. Chance here is counting drops since Cata release (about 5 months) but the tokens drop since 4.1 (roughly 1 month) so the chance is pretty screwed. My guess is somewhere around 30%. But hey, you can have 2 pieces in 1 drop according the few posts above yours.", "date": "2011-05-27T07:28:13-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-05-27T07:33:22-05:00", 1, "Alisarian"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 41, "id": 1431103, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "616836", "body": "Tanking in phase 1 can be just as terrible as it is for healers. When you're tanking, you don't have the luxury of being able to get Wind Bursted off in lieu of Squall Line hitting you. If you get Wind Bursted off, you get Electrocuted and you can't hit any CDs. You may even get knocked out of LoS from healers. At that point, you're dead, it's a wipe. Or sometimes you may be trying to dodge a tornado and run back in for Wind Burst, but you're not fast enough, get knocked off, and it's a wipe. This happened a few times in the 20+ attempts I just went through as a Blood DK, but still frustrating nonetheless.\n\nLooking forward to downing it so I never ever have to go back on any character again. Already this @#$% once as a Holy Priest. Thankfully, tanking in Phase 2 is easy mode assuming you know how to dodge tornadoes. If your tank can't dodge tornadoes, someone else has to tank Al'Akir.", "date": "2011-05-31T00:38:18-05:00", "rating": 5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-05-31T00:39:20-05:00", 1, "616836"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 42, "id": 1431908, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "837005", "body": "We are trying to beat him every week a day, but can't pass on phase3.\r\n\r\nPhase 1 is easy mode, practiced a lot, phase 2 is easier. But when we hit phase3 and fly to his head, we live maximum for 30 sec. First cloud come and the raid is dead... We moving fast down etc. we lose 100% hp in 1-2 seconds.\r\n\r\nWhat should we change? Thanks.", "date": "2011-06-01T06:41:41-05:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
