{"commentv2": 1, "number": 48, "id": 1476608, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "DeathCale", "body": "As of Patch 4.2 there is a bug where Acid Rain no longer stacks. This makes Phase 2 trivial and nearly impossible to die on.", "date": "2011-07-22T06:59:20-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Who was gonna die from 500 damage per sec already ? It does way too low damage and wont deal much damage unless p2 takes like 2 mins or so.", "creationdate": "2011-08-12T16:38:58-05:00", "id": 258233, "rating": -1, "commentid": 1476608, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Towerarcher", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Actually not a bug and a documented change in 4.2 as part of the T11 nerfing.", "creationdate": "2011-08-23T00:12:44-05:00", "id": 260145, "rating": 1, "commentid": 1476608, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "KuniZyrekai", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "[quote]Acid Rain now stacks every 20 seconds, up from 15.[/quote] That makes me think this was actually a bug as it doesn't say that it no longer stacks anywhere in the patch notes.", "creationdate": "2011-08-29T17:37:48-05:00", "id": 261426, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1476608, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "DeathCale", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 49, "id": 1502922, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "GeneralK", "body": "Nerfed Al'akir\r\n\r\nPhase1: spread out and only stack in for wind burst. it'll knock u off\r\n\r\ntanks must pass through every squal line effectivly. otherwise Al will mass spam electrocute and kill everyone. this is essential. even if u must back away for a few seconds dont let urself get caught in a tornado.\r\n\r\nphase2: kill stormlings asap. they spawn bout 10-15 seconds inbetween anyway so u can stack 30 second feedback easily. acid rain doesnt do any dmg anymore\r\n\r\np3: stack high up then go lower when clouds appear.. etc... same fight basically.\r\n\r\np3 can still #$%^up.. jus be careful.", "date": "2011-08-25T04:46:33-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 50, "id": 1571354, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "staron", "body": "I have done this 4-5 times now and I still do not think it is worth doing. I agree that the way the wind bursts interleave with the tornadoes can result in players dieing or getting very frustrated in Phase 1. Phase 2 is much more manageable and controllable. Phase 3 is a joke. 3 out of the 4 times I have done it, 80% of the raid was dead at the time of the boss kill. You think you are inside the lightning but you take no damage. You think you are safely away and you get whacked. Maybe one day we will come back as level 195 and do it for a laugh. Currently it is a joke.", "date": "2011-11-13T15:55:26-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
