{"commentv2": 1, "number": 65, "id": 2028638, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Mathaylla", "body": "Post-6.0.2 stat squish, the fight is mostly tank-and-spank for an ilvl 527 guardian druid. Popped Berserk at the start of the fight, to build up rage, in case I needed more self-heals with Frienzied Regen. Used Savage Defense, Survival Instincts and Barkskin, just to avoid taking unnecessary AoE damage, still a good idea to avoid lightning clouds in phase 3 - they hurt!", "date": "2014-11-12T20:41:57-06:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
