{"commentv2": 1, "number": 72, "id": 2546463, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "Gimi987", "body": "In first kill after patch 7.3.5 I killed Al'Akir very fast and did not get the flying buff and was unable to loot the crystal.  Was not a problem before this patch.", "date": "2018-01-17T18:12:26-06:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Same thing just happened to me : ( Did you make a ticket or did the loot fairy mail it to you?", "creationdate": "2018-01-18T07:49:02-06:00", "id": 1094717, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2546463, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "howlingstar", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Same...........", "creationdate": "2018-01-18T11:23:45-06:00", "id": 1094754, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2546463, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Nurmat", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Same thing happened to me, Hearth out, get back to instance and you'll have the flying buff when you enter, and will be able to reach the loot crystal.", "creationdate": "2018-01-19T00:16:54-06:00", "id": 1094900, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2546463, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Morneau", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I did make a ticket. No idea if fixed but I have been killing it more slowly since with no problems getting the buff.", "creationdate": "2018-02-02T18:22:51-06:00", "id": 1097734, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2546463, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Gimi987", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I just killed him, I got the flying buff and didnt have any issues, seems the bug has been fixed", "creationdate": "2018-05-21T10:11:12-05:00", "id": 1113318, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2546463, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "GanjalfDebaked", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 73, "id": 2546865, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Morneau", "body": "I was unable to loot Al'Akir in my first kill post-patch 7.3.5.  Attempting to leap to another platform would cause me to fall, get picked up by a whirlwind and deposited back on the platform I jumped from.  There was no ability to fly, and reach the loot crystal.\r\n\r\nI hearthed to Golden Lantern, took the SW portal, and then the Uldum portal.  Flew back to the instance and when I entered the instance, I had the flying buff and could then loot the crystal.  GL getting your mount. M", "date": "2018-01-19T00:15:43-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 74, "id": 2866083, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "clo4life", "body": "Killed him far too fast on 25H.  No loot was visible even with flying.  Turns out the Postmaster immediately mails you what you would have received, so there's no need to worry about not getting anything.", "date": "2019-01-15T03:10:01-06:00", "rating": 3, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 1214446, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "10128", "body": "Have killed a good thirty of these mobs (they have about 6 or 7 spawn points, you can't really chain them), and have had no luck in dropping Volatile Air. Am not sure the 28% drop rate is accurate at all.\n\nEDIT : by now, with more data received, the visible droprate has changed to 12%, which seems a lot more accurate.\n\nI would advice grinding these mobs for air however, you would probably be better off grinding airs of the Hyjal mobs (there's more of them) or the Twilight mobs (higher drop chance).", "date": "2010-12-08T09:15:24-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "not sure, killed 13 in a row with no drop then got 2x air twice... well within variance I guess, will keep testing.", "creationdate": "2010-12-08T18:16:32-06:00", "id": 465834, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1214446, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "36053", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "still somewhat anecdotal but i'd estimate the drop rate somewhere around 15-20% after 30 mins here.", "creationdate": "2010-12-08T18:44:44-06:00", "id": 465839, "rating": 3, "commentid": 1214446, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "36053", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2010-12-12T03:39:24-06:00", 1, "10128"]}
