{"commentv2": 1, "number": 3, "id": 1234357, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "66635", "body": "Farmed these for 120 minutes, killed exactly 340 of them and got 60 Volatile Airs, which is about 17.6% droprate. This seems to be in line with the reported droprate (it's 12%*(1+2)/2=18%). Also used a [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=58488]Potion of Treasure Finding[/url] for the latter 60 minutes and got 8 [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=67539]Tiny Treasure Chests[/url]. Overall a great farming spot, considering the price of Volatile Airs.", "date": "2010-12-14T22:35:45-06:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
