{"commentv2": 1, "number": 6, "id": 1242570, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "emmasteadman", "body": "I farmed about 50 of these and didn't get one single volatile air, the drop rate is considerably a lot lower than reported.", "date": "2010-12-18T07:08:08-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Think they just nerfed the drop rate on these mobs. Farmed on them a few days ago and I got a stack in about 4-5 hours (200 items), but today I got 1 in 60 mobs.  [b]Edit: After 5:30 hours and 621 kills, I got 121 of Volatile Airs.[/b]  [i]Edit2: guessing about % removed, indeed I was wrong doing maths at 6am in the morning.[/i]  I went there for another farming session. Farmed about 1200 mobs in 8 hours and only got 1 stack (200) of Volatile Air, lots of greens (27), and 2 random world drops, [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=52496]Design: Jeweler's Emerald Monocle[/url] and [url=http://www.wo", "creationdate": "2010-12-18T07:08:09-06:00", "id": 468859, "rating": 5, "commentid": 1242570, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Znuff", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "121 drops from 621 kills is about 19.5%, not 5%.", "creationdate": "2010-12-21T23:03:18-06:00", "id": 206803, "rating": 4, "commentid": 1242570, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "741196", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I like how people do these tests but can't do the math to make a proper calculation.", "creationdate": "2010-12-24T16:33:31-06:00", "id": 470275, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1242570, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "109627", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
