{"commentv2": 1, "number": 9, "id": 1252647, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Etreum", "body": "Nerfed fer sure.  I just killed forty and not a single drop.\n\nI just did another thirty and only got two airs, so that is two for seventy kills!  Barely a 3% drop rate.", "date": "2010-12-22T14:22:19-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "You can't base a % on such a small number of mobs... Your first try resulted in 0 out of 40 = 0% drop rate no? Second was 2 out of 30 = 6% drop rate... you can't be right both times :D  121 out of 621 = 19% drop rate - that's more like it...", "creationdate": "2011-01-18T07:23:00-06:00", "id": 216433, "rating": -1, "commentid": 1252647, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "tzakanel", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2010-12-22T14:33:49-06:00", 1, "Etreum"]}
