{"commentv2": 1, "number": 11, "id": 1255553, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "snifs", "body": "30 minutes of pharming netted me 20 volatile air.\n\nI'd get long periods of 0 drops, but the fact that half the drops i got gave me 2 airs, made up for it.\n\nI think that's more than a fair drop rate.\n\nThis was also during prime time with 5-8 other people pharming. Respawn was very fast though.\n\nDon't try running around on foot, kill then mount up. Also there are many spawns on the outskirts of the ruins that many people tend to forget about.", "date": "2010-12-23T20:45:23-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2010-12-23T20:46:10-06:00", 1, "snifs"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 12, "id": 1257861, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "664729", "body": "Started farming for 12 of these in and around Orsis in Uldum at 7:18a EST, was done at 7:42a EST. Took 8 minutes before first one dropped. They will sometimes drop 2 at a time. That's one per 2 minutes. Note there was no competition farming for these. HTH.", "date": "2010-12-25T06:46:51-06:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Farmed at about 4am EST.  It took 64 kills to get 2 volatile air.  By comparison, I got 3 greens and 2 treasure chests.  However, two days ago I farmed up 20 in the same area in about an hour.", "creationdate": "2010-12-26T03:41:07-06:00", "id": 470548, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1257861, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "369984", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
