{"commentv2": 1, "number": 31, "id": 1488286, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "354916", "body": "Alright I farmed these for one hour on Turalyon (Us) Horde. I fought for them with a pally but it wasn't much of a fight, being an arcane mage I pulled and killed them faster.\n\nBesides basic mage buffs. I used 1 [item=58488].\n\nI got\n30X [item=52328]\n169X [item=60485]\n26X [item=60486]\n7X [item=67539]\nAnd 5X Greens\n[item=24690]\n[item=55708]\n[item=55673]\n[item=55313]\n[item=55438]\n\nAnd in those 7X [item=67539]\nI received about 10 gold.\n5X [item=52328]\n3X [item=52325]\n1X [item=55771]\nand about 8 other assorted volatiles.\nOverall farming these was very easy once you get a route going, after all the treasure chests and drops I made out with a decent amount just for one hour. I also got 53 gold for the vendor trash. I am keeping the Boe greens just so I can disenchant them later. \n\nGood luck to those who farm, and always pick up a [item=58488], it makes everything easier.", "date": "2011-08-06T00:29:10-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-08-06T00:33:30-05:00", 1, "354916"]}
