{"commentv2": 1, "number": 33, "id": 1532940, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "BrknSoul", "body": "As of 02-Oct-11, these mobs still drop [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=52328]Volatile Air[/url]. Farmed them for an hour with [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=58488]Potion of Treasure Finding[/url]. I recieved the following;\r\n\r\n10 stacks of [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=60485]Crackling Crystals[/url]/[url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=60486]Shimmering Shards[/url]\r\n4 Junk Items\r\n6 Green Items\r\n36 [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=52328]Volatile Air[/url]\r\n9 [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=67539]Tiny Treasure Chests[/url]", "date": "2011-10-02T04:45:39-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 34, "id": 1586950, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "what3ver212", "body": "Farmed these tonight for Volatile Air, and got the following.\r\n\r\n192 x Crackling Crystals/Shimmering Shards\r\n33 x Volatile Air\r\n2 greens and about 6 other grey drops.\r\n\r\nIt's frustrating in the beginning as around the first 30 or so I killed didn't drop any.  Also, I noticed that they tend to drop 2 (and 1 dropped 3) more often, so the kills/drops per mob are even more skewed taking that into effect.  \r\n\r\nIf you're going to farm these for the Air then just be patient, they eventually drop.  You may have to kill 40 before you see your first one, but they drop.", "date": "2011-12-02T00:19:10-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 35, "id": 1632910, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Keepertje8", "body": "[b]1000g per hour?[/b]\n\nFarmed these for exactly one hour with a [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=58488]Potion of Treasurefinding[/url]. Some competition, but even with two farmers, you will not spend more than 3-4 seconds between each mob. 3-5 seconds to kill a mob as an Arcane Mage (ilvl390):\n\n7 greys\n43 [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=52328]Volatile Air[/url]\n6 greens\n240 [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=60485]Crackling Crystals[/url]\n44 [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=60486]Shimmering Shards[/url]\n15 [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=67539]Tiny Treasure Chests[/url]\n\nTrash and all vendored for 90g. Gold in chests was 40g. Greenies sold for 60g.\n4 stacks of [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=53010]Embersilk Cloth[/url] from the chests (360g), which can be doubled if you play the AH.\nSome more volatiles and other stuff from the chest. Volatiles sold for 700g (15g/Air + some from the chests). This is much lower than the 24g that Wowhead lists.\n\n[b]Yes, you can indeed make 1000g/hour here, even on a server with a lot of demand (like mine), with a [url=http://www.wowhead.com/item=58488]Potion of Treasurefinding[/url], and even more if you play the AH.[/b]", "date": "2012-02-28T08:59:41-06:00", "rating": -2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2012-02-28T09:00:35-06:00", 1, "Keepertje8"]}
